                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Sync Product Data into your Sales CRM</h3>
                    <span class="card-text">Get all your product data in your CRM tool and track user activity. Bucket users based on their activity and improve product adoption. Prevent users from churning by identifying issues in adoption.  </span>
                  </div>
