                      </div>
                    </figure>
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <h3 class="card-title">Build 360 View of Customer and Sync-up Sales CRM</h3>
                    <span class="card-text">Having access to siloed data from different tools in your stack which can be synced with your Sales CRM, you can understand your customers better with every vantage point.</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6 col-12  mb-7 mb-md-0">
                <div class="card resource-card use-cases-card">
                  <div class="card-img-top">
                    <figure class="embed-responsive use-cases-card-image-wrap mb-0">
